reviewText: I got both volumes as a gift and I liked them a lot. They are very rare horror films you won't find easily. They exist under many different names since they were made. All in all I recommend them to people like me who likes old, rare scifi or horror movies.
These are not actual titles, these are older movies just repackaged to try and take your money, in hopes of something rare. Don't be taken. Noone should make this mistake, I already made it for you.
